metadata.name: CATX_001.exe
metadata.description:
CAT ON A SYNTHESISER IN SPACE (001)

If you feel down today ...
just remember ...
somewhere in space ...
there's a cat ...
sat on a synth ...
making music just for you <3

These 1st few notes were composed by Luna, in space, using just her mind. She has been dreaming for over 5 minutes. Still no end in sight. We may be here for a very long time.

Art & Music by 8BitFantasy <3
